Package fr.prodrivers.bukkit.commons.parties

Enum Class PartyMessage

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<PartyMessage>
fr.prodrivers.bukkit.commons.parties.PartyMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<PartyMessage>, Constable
public enum PartyMessage extends Enum<PartyMessage>
Describe a list of possible party messages Party messages are triggered by the party manager, the party implementation is responsible for sending the actual message to the players. Messages
